			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				This system also caterers for each language's cultures differences such as:
			</p>
			<ul class="center">
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">pluralisations</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Genders</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Punctuation</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft"><abbr title="Right To Left">RTL</abbr> / <abbr title="Left To Right">LTR</abbr></li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Making the UI responsive to extreme string lengths</li>
			</ul>

			<h3 class="center reveal fromRight">Optimisation</h3>
			<p class="center reveal fromLeft">
				As our game has to run on low spec mobile devices it is critical that we test and optimize the performance of are app on devices regularly to maintain a shippable build.
			</p>
			<ul class="center">
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Profiling</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Cleaning up garbage allocations</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Caching</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">Pooling</li>
				<li class="left reveal fromLeft">reducing Code run time</li>
			</ul>


			<h3 class="center reveal fromBottom">As well As much more...</h3>
